text: Constantin Bușoiu (born 3 June 1941) is a Romanian wrestler. He competed in the men's Greco-Roman +97 kg at the 1968 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1941 births Category:Living people Category:Romanian male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of Romania Category:Wrestlers at the 1968 Summer Olympics Category:People from Dâmbovița County
